You'll see in the following videos what I mean when I say that

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:37.840
linear algebra topics tend to revolve around these two fundamental operations,

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:40.710
vector addition and scalar multiplication.

00:03:40.710 --> 00:03:43.849
So, they're your vector basics and in the next video,

00:03:43.849 --> 00:03:47.275
I'll start getting into some pretty neat concepts surrounding vectors like span,

00:03:47.275 --> 00:03:50.550
basis and linear dependence. See you then.

